They essentially made a Dollar General bootleg of their own logo for some reason.Either way tho it don't matter. Doesn't effect the games of Roblox and in my case if I'm really bothered by the change I can simply use the Stylus extension to change the look of the site to match my preferences. There's bound to be a style to rectify the current logo some time soon.
